data.description: Situated on 1/2 acre preserve, 545 Willow Walk is more than a home, it's a sanctuary.   The elegant courtyard, boardwalks, balconies and lanai give ample space to enjoy the natural habitat that embraces this home.  Inside, the impressive architectural design and custom touches include a stunning kitchen and a dining room fit for a royalty.  Each of the 3 En Suite bedrooms boast unique features:  a private balcony or grand french doors; but the piece de resistance is the owner's suite with expansive windows that overlook the preserve, a cozy fireplace and a bathroom better described as a Spa.  Best of all, you will feel miles away from everyone yet still enjoy living minutes from fine restaurants, historic beaches and the oldest city in the USA.  Welcome Home.
